Your zeal is noted, friend, but your Light requires refinement. As the acting officiator of the Trials of Osiris, Saint-14 has assessed the necessary requirements for entry. His assessment has set the entry bar at a measurable Power of 1270. While every Guardian has strength in their own right, some do not yet have the battle experience to operate seamlessly in a Trials fireteam.

Reach Power 1270, acquire Valor Legend rank, and defeat opponents in Elimination to participate in the Trials of Osiris.
